data.description: Move-in ready! This beautiful two-bedroom end unit townhome is just three-years-old. It features a beautiful kitchen with a large island, breakfast bar and walk-in pantry. Refrigerator remains. The open-concept living area gives you plenty of space for relaxation and entertainment. Upstairs, you'll find two generously sized bedrooms, each with its own bathroom. The primary bathroom features a large soaking tub with a separate shower and a walk-in closet. A custom accent wall was added in the primary bedroom, highlighting the high ceilings. Enjoy the large patio and covered front porch. Large storage closet located off of the patio. Two assigned parking spots. This neighborhood is conveniently located, with easy access to I-24 and a quick commute to Nashville. Close to the new Tanger Outlets and walking distance of the Global Mall. Ask about financing deal with Steadfast. Back on the market due to buyer financing - already went through inspection and report was clean.
